window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Spencer Quinn follows the critical success of his <i>\"New York Times</i> best-selling <i>Dog on It</i> with this second mystery starring hapless private investigator Bernie and his four-legged partner Chet, a K-9 school dropout. </p> <p>While Bernie continues his struggle to pay the bills, Chet - with his sharp nose and even sharper teeth - keeps bringing down the perps. Told from Chet's perspective and featuring the humorous ramblings of a dog, <i>Thereby Hangs a Tail</i> is another winner.</p>"; 
